data.description: Beautiful, completely remodeled Bungalow. This home has been gutted to the studs within the last 2 years. Features include a brand-new kitchen, new granite counter tops, white shaker cabinets, backsplash, lots of cupboard space & bay window. Premium vinyl plank floors in kitchen & living room, recessed lighting throughout. Both bathrooms are fully updated, Neutral decor throughout entire house with an open floor concept between the kitchen and living room. The home also includes a large detached 2 1/2 car garage less than 2yrs old with a fully fenced yard, all new concrete, newer windows, siding, C/A, & Furnace. Basement offers glass block windows, 2 bedrooms with full bathroom and an egress window. Don't miss the chance to make this your own. Schedule a viewing today!
